Package edu.rit.classfile.unittest

Package edu.rit.classfile.unittest contains unit test programs that demonstrate how to use the RIT Classfile Library.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Matrix Interface Matrix simply defines a few methods with array arguments for testing class StubSynthesizer.
 

Class Summary
GenTest02 Class GenTest02 demonstrates how the RIT Classfile Library can be used to synthesize a simple class.
MapStubTest Class MapStubTest is a main program that exercises the Stub Synthesizer in class StubSynthesizer.
MatrixStubTest Class MatrixStubTest is a main program that exercises the Stub Synthesizer in class StubSynthesizer.
StubSynthesizer Class StubSynthesizer demonstrates how the RIT Classfile Library can be used to synthesize a stub that implements a given interface.
Test02  
TestTest02 Class TestTest02 is a main program that tests the class synthesized by the GenTest02 main program.
 

Package edu.rit.classfile.unittest Description

Package edu.rit.classfile.unittest contains unit test programs that demonstrate how to use the RIT Classfile Library. The RIT Classfile Library is contained in package edu.rit.classfile.

RIT Classfile Library Version 02-Jul-2002
